@startuml 20-ladder-b-device-cicd
title Ladder B — Device / PWA CI/CD\ntouchscreen-ux · ADR-007 · ADR-016\nDo not conflate with Ladder A (GHA → ECR → ECS)

left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1565C0
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

rectangle "feature/*\nbranch" as Feat #BBDEFB
rectangle "PR → staging\n(never from main)" as PR #90CAF9
rectangle "CI\nlint · tsc · test · build" as CI #81D4FA
rectangle "Netlify\nbranch preview\nweb-only" as Netlify #FFE0B2
rectangle "Human TTV filesync\n→ QA / canary" as TTVQA #A5D6A7
rectangle "Promote\nstaging → main" as Promo #CE93D8
rectangle "Human TTV filesync\n→ prod fleet" as TTVProd #80CBC4
rectangle "Esper MDM\ndevice tags" as Esper #B39DDB

Feat --> PR
PR --> CI
CI --> Netlify
CI --> TTVQA
TTVQA --> Promo
Promo --> TTVProd
TTVProd --> Esper

note bottom of CI
  **Confirmed:** ci.yml
  (touchscreen-ux)
end note

note bottom of Netlify
  **Confirmed:** web preview only
  ≠ device path
end note

note bottom of TTVQA
  **Confirmed:** human-triggered
  clear TTV cache after deploy
end note

note top of TTVProd
  Version stamp in logs:
  [touchscreen-ux] app version:
  <hash> (<build time>)
end note

note bottom of Esper
  **Confirmed:** Esper + TTV player
  brand via device tags
end note

legend right
  |= Maturity |= Meaning |
  | Confirmed | Branch ladder + CI + Netlify ≠ device;\nhuman TTV; Esper tags (ADR-007, 016) |
  | Note | Clear TTV cache after every filesync;\nversion stamp verifies live build |
  | Out of scope | **No** ECR · **No** ECS · **No** Terraform\n(Ladder A only) |
endlegend

@enduml
